</table><p>This medical device is designed with high clinical-grade materials. Key technical features: <strong>Material</strong>: Thermosensitive transparent medical PVC. <strong>Cuff</strong>: Yes, low profile, low pressure / high volume (BPHV). <strong>Bevel</strong>: Murphy type with atraumatic eye. <strong>X-ray Opacity</strong>: Continuous radio-opaque line throughout the length. <strong>Clinical Use</strong>: Prolonged ventilatory tracheal intubation.</p>' WHERE id = 16;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Spinal Anesthesia Needle (Pencil Point) (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Spinal Anesthesia Needle (Pencil Point) is a state-of-the-art medical instrument designed to offer excellent performance and safety during spinal anesthesia procedures. Made from high-quality 304 stainless steel, it guarantees biocompatibility and exceptional resistance to corrosion. Its ergonomic design with a pencil-shaped tip allows for atraumatic penetration, thereby minimizing the risk of post-procedural complications and ensuring optimal patient comfort.</p>

<p>This medical device is sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), a process that ensures purity and the absence of contaminants. Maintaining impeccable sterility is crucial to prevent nosocomial infections. Each needle is individually packaged in a sterile wrapper, facilitating its use in intensive clinical or hospital environments.</p>

