UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Coloplast Easicath Pediatric Catheter (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Coloplast Easicath Pediatric Catheter embodies a modern and safe catheterization solution specifically designed for the needs of young patients. Made of phthalate-free medical-grade PVC, this catheter ensures optimal biocompatibility, thereby minimizing the risk of allergic reactions or irritations. Free from phthalates, the material complies with strict regulations on pediatric medical devices, ensuring confident use in children.</p>

<p>To ensure the highest level of sterility, each catheter is rigorously sterilized using ethylene oxide (EO), a method recognized for its ability to eliminate microorganisms while preserving material integrity. This method ensures each product presentation is ready for use, offering immediate safety for patients and healthcare professionals.</p>

<p>The Easicath Catheter offers a range of dimensions from 6 to 12 Fr, allowing clinicians to easily select the appropriate size according to the child''s age and physiology. Equipped with a rounded atraumatic tip, it ensures smooth passage and reduces the risk of trauma during insertion, making the procedure more comfortable for young patients. Each catheter is delivered in an individual sterile package for convenient and hygienic handling in care settings.</p>

