UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Vaginal Speculum (Greatcare) (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Greatcare Vaginal Speculum, listed under SKU: GRE-ABRAKQ, embodies the optimal balance between functionality and comfort for professional users. Made from medical-grade 304 stainless steel, this device ensures exceptional biocompatibility, preventing any form of irritation or adverse reaction during use. Its robust design guarantees long-term durability while maintaining excellent resistance to corrosion.</p>

<p>Specifically designed for professional use in clinical or hospital settings, this speculum is ethylene oxide (EO) sterilized, effectively eliminating microbial risks, thereby ensuring maximum protection and surgical safety. The sterile individual packaging enhances this safety, allowing healthcare professionals to maintain high infection control standards during gynecological procedures.</p>

<p>Equipped with a rounded tip, this speculum optimizes ergonomics and minimizes discomfort for patients, exemplifying an atraumatic approach during clinical examinations. With multi-size options, it meets the diverse requirements of various morphologies, facilitating personalized and precise usage. Its CE certification ensures compliance with rigorous European standards, thereby raising the standard of care and protecting user and patient safety.</p>

