UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath is a medical device specifically designed for external adaptation, providing a practical solution for patients suffering from urinary incontinence. Made from natural rubber latex, this penile cone ensures optimal biocompatibility. The product''s design emphasizes ergonomics, allowing for comfortable and uncompromised adaptation for the user. Available in various sizes (Small, Medium, Large), it meets the specific needs of each patient, ensuring a personalized fit.</p>
<p>Designed for professional use, whether in clinical or hospital environments, the Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath complies with CE certification, meeting safety and efficiency standards for medical use. Its individual packaging preserves its properties until the time of use, although it is not sterile. It is therefore essential to rigorously follow standard hygiene procedures in clinical settings to ensure patient safety.</p>
<p>Key features of this product include a non-traumatic design that minimizes the risk of skin injury during application and removal. It is vital for practitioners to have a product that provides reliability and simplicity of use to maintain a high level of care. With its specifications, the Coloplast Conveen Penile Sheath stands out as a top choice for healthcare professionals seeking high-quality incontinence management solutions.</p>
