</table><p>This medical device is designed with high clinical-quality materials. Key technical features: <strong>Material</strong>: Latex-free silicone, self-adhesive. <strong>Attachment</strong>: Integrated skin-friendly acrylic adhesive. <strong>Design</strong>: Anti-kink system (ensures continuous flow). <strong>Clinical Use</strong>: Male urinary incontinence.</p>' WHERE id = 505;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Laryngoscope Macintosh – Cullinan | Intubation', description_en = '<p>The Laryngoscope Macintosh - Cullinan for intubation is a high-precision medical device designed to meet the rigorous demands of healthcare professionals during orotracheal intubation procedures. Made from superior-quality 304 stainless steel, this instrument ensures optimal biocompatibility and corrosion resistance, thereby providing exceptional durability even after multiple uses.</p>
<p>Its ergonomic design promotes easy and precise handling, reducing clinicians'' fatigue during prolonged interventions. The 120 mm blade''s ergonomic and atraumatic finish minimizes the risk of injury to the patient''s delicate tissues. Conforming to CE standards, the laryngoscope meets international safety and performance standards, making it a reliable choice for medical facilities.</p>
<p>Designed to be fully autoclavable, this laryngoscope ensures effective high-temperature sterilization, essential for preventing nosocomial infections. Each unit is packaged in an individual sterile pack, ensuring a high level of purity until the moment of use. This laryngoscope is the result of advanced engineering, offering optimized visibility and guaranteeing precise and safe intervention every use.</p>
