UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Pharmafix® — Soft Cloth Fixation Dressing', description_en = '<p class=''text-gray-900 text-base font-semibold''>Pharmafix® — Soft Cloth Fixation Dressing is designed for healthcare professionals demanding a high-performance fixation solution. Composed of soft non-woven fabric, this product offers optimal support while preserving patient comfort. The biocompatibility of its hypoallergenic acrylic adhesive ensures exceptional skin tolerance, minimizing the risk of irritation or allergic reactions. Thanks to its ergonomic structure, Pharmafix® provides atraumatic application, thus preserving the integrity of the patient''s skin during dressing changes.</p>

<p class=''text-gray-900 text-base font-semibold''>Compliant with European CE standards, Pharmafix® meets the strict demands of quality and safety, facilitating its use in clinical settings. Its large dimension of 10 cm x 10 m allows adaptation to various anatomical surfaces, easing the fixation of dressings and catheters, even in hard-to-reach areas. Non-sterile, this device is ideal for general use when sterile conditions are not imperative.</p>

<p class=''text-gray-900 text-base font-semibold''>Packaged in boxes of 12 rolls, Pharmafix® ensures easy stock management and immediate availability within the hospital environment. Its lightness combined with its flexibility allows precise and adaptable handling during interventions. Moreover, its balanced adhesiveness contributes to reliable fixation without damaging the skin surface during removal.</p>

