UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Subglottic Intubation Tube 5', description_en = '<p>The <strong>Subglottic Intubation Tube 5</strong>, with SKU <em>RUS100380-000050</em>, is an essential medical device specifically designed to meet the rigorous demands of intensive care. Made from <em>premium medical-grade silicone</em>, this tube ensures optimal biocompatibility and minimizes potential allergic reactions, thereby ensuring patient safety during medical intervention.</p>
<p>With <em>ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization</em>, our tube offers a sterile, ready-to-use solution, vital for sensitive medical environments. Featuring an <em>atraumatic tip</em>, it is specifically designed to reduce the risk of tissue trauma during insertion, which is crucial for ensuring safe and effective procedures.</p>
<p>The tube measures <em>70 cm in length</em> with a diameter of <em>5 mm</em>, making it perfectly suited for subglottic use. Classified under <em>CE class III</em>, it meets all necessary compliance standards, providing medical professionals with complete confidence in the product''s integrity and performance.</p>
