UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Sterile Latex Examination Gloves, Powder-Free, Single Use', description_en = '<p>The sterile latex examination gloves, powder-free and single-use, are designed to meet the rigorous demands of modern clinical settings. Made from high-quality natural latex, these gloves provide exceptional biocompatibility and minimize the risk of skin allergic reactions due to their powder-free composition. Each pair is sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring a level of asepsis compliant with the stringent standards of medical procedures.</p>
<p>With refined ergonomics, these one-size gloves fit optimally to the user''s morphology, offering a comfortable and secure fit. Their stretchability allows for precise and atraumatic movements, essential for a wide range of medical applications. The rolled cuff provides an additional barrier against accidental contamination, enhancing the safety and efficacy of personal protective equipment.</p>
<p>Fully compliant with CE certification according to EN455 standard, these gloves are designed for various clinical applications and are particularly suited for procedures where high tactile sensitivity is crucial. Packaged in boxes of 100 units, they ensure efficient and hygienic stock management in hospital environments.</p>
