</table>' WHERE id = 567;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Tracheofix Kit with Cuff (Multi-Size)', description_en = '<p>The Tracheofix Kit with Cuff is an advanced tracheal intubation solution designed to meet the stringent demands of modern clinical interventions. Made from medical-grade polyvinyl chloride (PVC), this device ensures superior biocompatibility, reducing the risk of adverse reactions for the patient. Its design includes an optimized beveled tip for atraumatic insertion, thus minimizing tissue trauma and facilitating rapid and efficient intubation.</p>
<p>Available in sizes ranging from 14G to 24G, it offers great flexibility for a variety of clinical applications tailored to the specific needs of patients. Each kit is sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring optimal protection against infections. The device''s ergonomics are enhanced by an inflatable cuff that ensures perfect sealing, optimizing ventilation and reducing the risk of air leaks.</p>
<p>Conforming to the rigorous CE standards of the European Union, the Tracheofix Kit is distinguished by its individual packaging. Each element of the kit is meticulously sterilized and presented in easy-to-open packaging to facilitate quick and efficient use in emergency situations. This attention to detail and regulatory requirements highlights the commitment to safety and clinical efficacy.</p>
<table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
