UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Scalpel Blade (Multi-Size)', description_en = '<p>The SW158511 scalpel blades, crafted with precision from 304 stainless steel, offer exceptional performance essential for sophisticated surgical procedures. With superior biocompatibility, these blades ensure minimal interaction with living tissues, reducing the risk of adverse reactions during surgical interventions. The sharp design of these blades enables maximized surgical precision, facilitating clean and precise incisions, thus reducing tissue trauma.</p>
<p>The scalpel blade is rigorously sterilized with ethylene oxide (EO), ensuring that each unit is free from harmful microorganisms and ready for immediate use. Each blade is individually packaged, maintaining its sterile integrity until it is ready to be used. CE certified, these blades meet the highest standards for medical devices, assuring clinicians of the safety and efficacy of their instrumentation.</p>
<p>Available in various sizes from 15 to 23, these single-use scalpel blades are optimized for clinical use and are ideal for precision surgeries where quality and performance must never be compromised. Their ergonomic design promotes attractive handling, ensuring a comfortable grip during prolonged procedures. These blades are specifically designed for single-use, reducing the risk of cross-contamination.</p>
