UPDATE product SET name_en = '1ml Luer Slip Syringe with 27G Needle', description_en = '<p>The 1 ml Luer Slip Syringe with 27G needle is a high-precision medical device designed for demanding clinical procedures. It offers perfect integration of functionality and biocompatibility, optimizing the experience for practitioners and comfort for patients. The syringe is equipped with a Luer Slip tip that ensures a quick and reliable connection, minimizing leakage risks. The 1 ml capacity is ideal for precision injections, especially in clinical testing or specialized treatments.</p>
<p>The 27G needle, made from 304 medical-grade stainless steel, guarantees atraumatic penetration and excellent motion control, thereby reducing discomfort for the patient. With ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, the device maintains impeccable sterility, a crucial element for infection prevention in clinical or hospital settings.</p>
<p>CE certified, this product adheres to strict health and safety standards, ensuring not only regulatory compliance but also peace of mind for practitioners. Designed for professional use, this device is ergonomically designed to precisely meet specialists'' needs, ensuring smooth and efficient handling during interventions. With its notable features, the syringe ensures optimal performance and reliable professional dependability.</p>
