UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Wiscope Flexible Single-Use Cystoscope', description_en = '<p>The Wiscope Flexible Single-Use Cystoscope, SKU: OTU-C380RR, is a state-of-the-art medical device designed to provide an optimal clinical experience through advanced engineering and high-quality materials. Crafted from 304 stainless steel, noted for its exceptional biocompatibility and resistance to all forms of corrosion, this cystoscope ensures reliable performance. Its single-use nature eliminates cross-infection risks, ensuring maximum patient safety.</p><p>This cystoscope features a flexible tip that minimizes trauma during delicate and sensitive endoscopic procedures. The flexibility enhances ergonomics, allowing smoother and atraumatic insertion, increasing patient comfort while maintaining excellent clinician visibility. The sterile individual packaging, ensured by ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, means each unit is ready for immediate use, offering substantial time savings in dynamic care environments.</p><p>The Wiscope is CE-certified, guaranteeing it meets stringent European safety and performance standards. Its compact dimensions, 3.5 mm by 40 cm, make it suitable for a variety of clinical applications, allowing adaptability in diverse surgical settings. Its design emphasizes single-use, making it not only easy to handle but also cost-effective in terms of use and maintenance.</p><table class="w-full text-left border-collapse"><thead><tr><th class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Specification</th><th class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-t border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Material</td><td class="border-t border-b border-gray-300 py-2">304 Stainless Steel</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Sterilization</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Ethylene Oxide (EO)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">CE / ISO Compliance</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">CE Certification</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Clinical Use</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Single-use, atraumatic endoscopies</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Features</td><td class="border-b border-gray-300 py-2">Diameter 3.5 mm x Length 40 cm, Flexible tip, Ergonomic use</td></tr></tbody></table>' WHERE id = 531;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Gynecological Examination Kit', description_en = '<p>The Gynecological Examination Kit (SKU: KIT-GYN-001) marks a significant advancement in gynecological clinical practice with its ergonomic design, facilitating both diagnostic and therapeutic procedures. Made from high-quality medical-grade plastic, this kit ensures exceptional biocompatibility, reducing the risk of adverse reactions for patients. Each component is crafted to offer maximum comfort for the practitioner while ensuring an atraumatic experience for the patient.</p><p>The kit''s sterility is maintained through ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, a reliable process ensuring the complete elimination of microorganisms, adhering to the highest health safety standards. The speculum, of standard medium size, is ideal for most patients and is designed for single use to prevent cross-contaminations and ensure optimal infection control.</p><p>The kit is carefully packaged in a sterile individual package, simplifying handling and preserving sterility until usage. The brush included in the kit features a soft nylon-tipped end, ideal for homogenous sample collection without epithelial cell disruption. CE 0123 certification confirms this kit meets regulatory requirements, guaranteeing safe and effective clinical use.</p><table class="w-full border-collapse"><thead><tr><th class="border-b py-2 px-4 text-left">Specification</th><th class="border-b py-2 px-4 text-left">Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Material</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Medical-grade plastic</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Sterilization</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Ethylene Oxide (EO)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">CE / ISO Compliance</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">CE 0123</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Clinical Use</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Single-use</td></tr><tr><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Features</td><td class="border-t py-2 px-4">Medium size speculum, Sterile individual packaging, Soft nylon-tip brush</td></tr></tbody></table>' WHERE id = 10003;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Urinary Catheterization Kit', description_en = '<p>The Urinary Catheterization Kit, model KIT-URO-001, is engineered to offer a premium medical solution for healthcare professionals requiring atraumatic and efficient bladder management. This meticulously crafted kit ensures a safe and comfortable patient experience. The catheter is made from soft silicone, a material known for its high biocompatibility and optimal comfort during prolonged insertion. This choice significantly reduces the risk of allergies and irritation, enabling prolonged use without complications.</p>

<p>The ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization process ensures complete microorganism elimination, providing maximum safety for medical interventions. The 2-liter collection bag capacity is ideal for efficient drainage management while minimizing the need for frequent emptying. Additionally, the kit includes a 10 ml syringe, allowing precise and controlled catheter state adjustment within the patient''s bladder, providing essential therapeutic flexibility to caregivers.</p>

<p>Equipped with a water-based anesthetic gel lubricant, this kit offers careful lubrication for easy insertion and removal, minimizing patient discomfort. The Foley 2-way catheter design enhances urinary flow and facilitates irrigation, ideal for short- and long-term applications. Each kit is sterilely packaged individually, offering peace of mind for both medical staff and patients by ensuring product integrity until application. Compliant with international CE and ISO standards, the KIT-URO-001 represents excellence in clinical innovations.</p>

