</table>' WHERE id = 10004;
UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Right Selective Intubation Catheter Kit Ch39', description_en = '<p>The <strong>Right Selective Intubation Catheter Kit Ch39</strong> is a highly innovative medical device designed to provide a reliable solution for selective intubation in demanding clinical settings. Made from <span class=''text-gray-700''>premium quality medical-grade PVC</span>, this device ensures exceptional biocompatibility and optimal patient comfort, while guaranteeing the robust resistance essential for safe interventions.</p>

<p>The device undergoes rigorous ethylene oxide (EO) sterilization, certifying microbial efficacy, thus ensuring its readiness for immediate clinical use. CE certification attests to its compliance with current safety and performance standards, positioning the product at the top of industry benchmarks.</p>

<p>Characterized by a length of 39 cm and a diameter of 6 mm, the kit is specifically designed for right pulmonary selective intubation. Its innovative beveled tip facilitates atraumatic insertion, promoting an ergonomic approach and reducing the risk of complications during the intubation process. Each unit is carefully packaged in a sterile individual package, ensuring its integrity until the point of use.</p>

