UPDATE product SET name_en = 'Greatcare Nasal Speculum (Multi-Sizes)', description_en = '<p>The Greatcare Nasal Speculum is designed to meet the demanding requirements of modern clinical and hospital environments with its construction from high-quality 304 stainless steel. This material is renowned for its exceptional biocompatibility, thus ensuring inert interaction with biological tissues and minimizing risks of allergic or inflammatory reactions in patients. The speculum''s design incorporates an ergonomic mechanism that facilitates handling by healthcare professionals, ensuring both safe and effective use.</p>
<p>The Nasal Speculum is sterilized by Ethylene Oxide (EO), providing the medical device with superior microbiological safety necessary for the prevention of nosocomial infections. With its rounded edges, this speculum offers atraumatic performance, thereby minimizing the risk of injury to delicate nasal tissues during examinations or procedures.</p>
<p>Available in multiple sizes, this product is CE certified, ensuring compliance with stringent European medical device standards. Each unit is individually wrapped in a sterile package, guaranteeing optimal hygiene until the moment of use. Intended for professional use in clinics and hospitals, the Greatcare Nasal Speculum is an essential tool for professionals committed to providing high-quality and safe care.</p>

